article_title: Winning $646,555 lottery ticket sold in Piscataway
article_text:
Buy Photo ~ (Photo: MyCentralJersey )Buy Photo Story Highlights Winning Jersey Cash 5 lottery sold at Quick Chek

$5,000 MegaMillions ticket sold in Middlesex Borough

A winning Jersey Cash 5 lottery ticket worth $646,555 was sold at Quick Chek, 191 Stelton Road.

The ticket was the only winner sold for the Oct. 25 drawing. The winning numbers were 8, 26, 28, 31 and 36.

A $5,000 Mega Millions ticket was sold at Middlesex Liquor Store, 708 Union Ave., Middlesex Borough, for the Oct. 24 drawing.

The winning ticket matched four white balls and the Gold Mega Ball. The winning numbers were 2, 14, 21, 28 and 55 with the Gold Mega Ball of 3.

The jackpot for Tuesday’s MegaMillions will be $252 million.

Staff Writer Mike Deak: 908-243-6607; mdeak@mycentraljersey.com
